一、类注释模板
-------------------------------------------------------------
/**
 * @desc:
 *
 * @author: Richy
 * @date: $date$ $time$
 */
------------------------------------------------------------

二、方法注释模板
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Abbreviation:*
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 *
  * @desc:
  *
  * @method: $method$
 $params$
  * @date:   $date$ $time$
  * @return: $returns$
  */

  $params$脚本：

  groovyScript("def result=''; def params=\"${_1}\".replaceAll('[\\\\[|\\\\]|\\\\s]', '').split(',').toList(); for(i = 0; i < params.size(); i++) {result+=' * @param:\\t' + params[i] + ': ' + ((i < params.size() - 1) ? '\\n' : '')}; return result", methodParameters())

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

三、注释示例：

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
/**
 * @desc:
 * 示例接口
 * @author: Richy
 * @date: 2020-12-27 18:27
 */
@RequestMapping("example")
@RestController
public class ExampleController {

    /**
     * @desc:
     * 查询用户详细信息
     * @method: queryUserInfo
     * @param:	name: 姓名
     * @param:	age: 年龄
     * @date:   2020-12-27 18:32
     * @return: java.lang.String
     */
    @PostMapping("info")
    public String queryUserInfo(String name,Integer age){
        return "getInfo";
    }
}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------